BEIJING , July 1 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- The People 's Liberation Army -LRB- PLA -RRB- and the Chinese People 's Armed Police Force have joined in the nationwide celebrations to greet the return of Hong Kong .
From midnight Monday till dawn today , offers and men of the General Departments of the PLA , and the PLA military area commands of Beijing , Lanzhou , Jinan , Nanjing and Chengdu and armed police forces watched or listened to the live broadcast of the ceremony of China 's resumption of the exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong and viewed a variety of song and dance and other theatrical performances.. They were particularly interested in the entry into Hong Kong of the armed forces posted there .
Many generals and military experts agreed that it would have been impossible for the army to march into Hong Kong if China had not grown so strong since the reform and opening up .
They expressed the hope that their fellow soldiers stationed in Hong Kong will strictly observe the Basic Law of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region -LRB- SAR -RRB- and the Law Concerning Stationing Troops to the Hong Kong SAR and perform their duties with flying colors .
